Package org.whispercomm.c2dm4j.async.handler

Interface Summary
AsyncHandlers A collection of MessageFilter, ResponseHandler, and ThrowableHandler objects used to automatically handle certain responses and errors in the asynchronous flow.
Context<T,E extends Enum<E>> Context associated with an object (i.e., Message, Response, or Throwable) in the asynchronous flow.
MessageFilter Interface for a message filter.
ResponseHandler<R extends Response> Interface for a response handler.
ThrowableHandler<T extends Throwable> Interface for an exception handler.
 

Class Summary
AsyncHandlersFactory Static factory methods to construct AsyncHandlers instances.
DeviceBackoffThrottle A message filter and response handler that implements per-device retry with backoff for DeviceQuotaExceeded responses.
GlobalBackoffThrottle A message filter and response handler that implements global retry with backoff for QuotaExceeded and ServiceUnavailable responses and delays messages to respect Retry-After headers.
 

Enum Summary
MessageDecision Enumeration of valid decisions for Message objects.
ResultDecision Enumeration of valid decisions for Response and Throwable objects.
